title: A Lineup Fit for a Champion | The Dantasy Football Podcast (Ep. 385)
description:
The Dannys select a surprising QB and a not-so-surprising WR on their winning daily fantasy lineup as four offensive powerhouses face off in the championship round.

Hosts: Danny Heifetz and Danny Kelly
